des:
Gymshark66 - Challenge yourself to change. 

To support you in your Gymshark66 pledges, we have created our own Amazon Alexa Skill to provide you with on-demand information, motivation & fun that is delivered by our very own athletes! We want to give our community a boost when you need it most and empower you to be the best version of yourself during #Gymshark66.

They say it takes 66 days to form a habit; we believe it takes 66 days to change your life.

We want you to form positive habits that will change your life for the better, and share your story with #Gymshark66 on social media. 

All you have to do - for 66 days - is try. Try for the first time, try something new or try 10% harder at something you already do. However you challenge yourself, for 66 days, the only thing you have to try is your best. 

66 days is enough time to change your life whenever you start, but what better time than the first of the first? 

Gymshark 66 kicks off January 1st 2021, but your challenge begins right now. It’s time to start thinking about what you’ll try for #Gymshark66, ready to make your pledge on social media to enter the challenge between December 8th and December 31st 2020. 

How to launch the skill?
- “Alexa, start Gymshark sixty six”
- “Alexa, launch Gymshark sixty six"

Challenges?
- Want more information about the weekly Gymshark66 challenges? Launch the skill and ask for challenges information

Motivation?
- We want to provide you with some much-needed motivation. Ask Alexa to provide you with some Gymshark motivation and listen to some of our athletes’ favourite motivational quotes!

Fun?
- Do you love testing your fitness knowledge? Challenge yourself with our very own quiz, including questions about fitness, health & Gymshark!
